column2: TD HOLDINGS, INC., formerly BAT GROUP, INC., is a China-based holding company principally involved in the used luxurious car leasing business that is conducted under the brand name Batcar. The Company provides a variety of brands and types of high-end cars for leasing. The Company primarily conducts its businesses in Beijing, Tianjin and Hebei, China.
No.1 Zhongying Commercial Plaza, Zhong Ying Road, Wujiang
